comments.body:
eugene,
 The patch looks good.

One minor nit:

{code}
 if (authInfo.contains(id) == false) {
           authInfo.add(id);
 }
{code}

can be replaced by:

{code}
 if (!authInfo.contains(id)) {
           authInfo.add(id);
        }
{code}

I can make the minor change and check it in. Let me know.
